question: Which restaurant is available within 110 kilometers in the south direction of Sea Life Aquarium Kansas City, Kansas City, MO?
sql:
WITH origin AS  (SELECT ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-94.5816 39.082158)',4326)::geography AS geometry)
SELECT * FROM pois, origin
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-94.5816 39.082158)',4326)::geography, 110000)
AND amenity = 'restaurant'
AND degrees(ST_Azimuth(origin.geometry, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN 157.5 AND 202.5;

answers.poi_name: South of Summit Taqueria and Tequila
